name: Losing Vol.1
description:
"Losing Vol.1" is the first 'wave' of "losing"
The photo series that I took in the sea of Pha Ngan island, Thailand
in the feeling of 'Losing' something

Losing myself to the feelings
Losing myself to the moments
Losing myself to the lost
Losing myself to the nature
Losing myself to the sea

But I won't let this beauty get lost
